<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Contact.Name},</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We have received the original bank mandate for IATA {<b>!Case.Country__c}.</b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Your request is being processed.&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">To enhance the security of your payments, IATA will test the bank mandate by transfering a penny to the new account details you provided:</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">In the case that the transfer is accepted by our bank, the account details will be effectively changed by IATA.</span></li><li><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">In the case that the penny transfer is rejected by our bank, we will inform you of the needed changes to your bank details.</span></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Kindly reminding you to keep your current bank details active until IATA will send you a confirmation that the bank account change has been successfully carried out, including the settlement date in which the new instruction will be effective.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We will contact you shortly.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Kind Regards,</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">{!Case.OwnerFullName}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Global Airline Participation Team</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Financial and Distribution Services</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">International Air Transport Association (IATA)</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">33, Route de l' Aeroport</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">1215 Geneve</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Switzerland</font></p>

